Code 1, 1A, 2B.

282
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:36,153
COMPUTER:
Self-destruct sequence activated.

283
00:16:40,759 --> 00:16:43,512
What are you gonna do, Sheldon,
blow up the apartment?

284
00:16:43,679 --> 00:16:44,998
That was my first thought.

285
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:47,720
But all my cool stuff is here.

286
00:16:47,879 --> 00:16:50,234
