287
00:16:50,399 --> 00:16:52,674
Unless Leonard
signs the new agreement...

288
00:16:52,839 --> 00:16:54,272
...in the next 41 seconds...

289
00:16:54,439 --> 00:16:58,034
...this computer will send an e-mail
to your parents in India...

290
00:16:58,240 --> 00:17:00,435
...saying
that you're in a secret relationship...

291
00:17:00,639 --> 00:17:04,075
...with the whiter-than-marshmallow-fluff
Leonard Hofstadter.

292
00:17:05,799 --> 00:17:07,755
-Oh, my God.
-What's the big deal?

293
00:17:07,919 --> 00:17:11,070
-Trust me, it's a big deal.
-They're gonna find out eventually...

294
00:17:11,239 --> 00:17:12,831
-...right?
-Yeah. Just not today.

295
00:17:12,999 --> 00:17:14,318
Twenty seconds.

296
00:17:14,479 --> 00:17:16,629
-Are you ashamed of me?
-Of course not.

297
00:17:16,799 --> 00:17:19,438
-Why can't we tell your parents?
-Please, don't push this.

298
00:17:19,599 --> 00:17:21,590
He does that all the time. Fifteen.

299
00:17:21,759 --> 00:17:24,637
-Okay, Sheldon, you win. Turn it off.
-No, he's bluffing.

300
00:17:24,799 --> 00:17:26,073
I never bluff. Ten.

301
00:17:26,239 --> 00:17:27,388
-lt's blackmail.
-Nine.

302
00:17:27,559 --> 00:17:29,834
-We give up.
-This is ridiculous.

303
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:32,958
It's a laptop with a full charge.
What do you see in him?

304
00:17:33,119 --> 00:17:35,758
-Give him what he wants or we're done.
-Really?

305
00:17:35,919 --> 00:17:37,318
-Two.
-Okay, I'll sign it.

306
00:17:38,120 --> 00:17:41,317
COMPUTER:
Self-destruct sequence aborted.

307
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:48,392
You may have gone to Cambridge,
but I am an honorary graduate...

308
00:17:48,559 --> 00:17:50,436
...of Starfleet Academy.

309
00:17:56,639 --> 00:17:58,231
