as a pillow...

324
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:53,233
...set your oven clock to the correct time
because it was driving me crazy...

325
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:55,789
...and I left.

326
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:58,073
Okay.

327
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:01,830
Don't really know
where we go from here.

328
00:19:03,199 --> 00:19:07,112
I suggest we treat our relationship
as if it were a crashed computer...

329
00:19:07,279 --> 00:19:10,351
